%table{class: "sections"}
  %tr
    %td{class: "section"}
      %h2 Latest Tournaments
      %ul{class: "home"}
        - @tournaments.each do |t|
          %li
            = link_to t.name, t
        %li= link_to "More...", tournaments_path
    %td{class: "section"}
      %h2 Latest News
      %ul{class: "home"}
        - @news_items.each do |n|
          %li
            = link_to n.headline, n
        %li= link_to "More...", news_items_path

#help
  %dl
    %dt How can I see my rating?
    %dd
      This functionality is still in development and should be ready early in 2012.
      Meanwhile, please continue to use the
      =link_to_icu "rating list", "ratings/list.php"
      on the main site.
    %dt How can I submit a tournament for rating?
    %dd
      - if !current_user
        First log in, then click Help again.
      - elsif can? :create, Upload
        Click Tournament &rarr; New.
      - else
        Please ask the
        = mail_to_icu
        to authorize your account for submissions.
    - unless current_user
      %dt How can I log in?
      %dd
        Go to the
        = link_to "Log in", log_in_path
        page where there is further help if you need it.
